  "texts": [
    "For example, the domain knowledge corresponding to the specific ISAC systems can be used to guide the design of neural networks, and the customized neural network is expected to overcome the drawbacks of general-purpose neural networks [282].",
    "Deep unfolding, as a representative of model-driven learning, unfolds the iterative algorithm into a neural network with learnable parameters, where each layer represents each iteration of the iterative algorithm.",
    "Moreover, the deep unfolding network outperforms traditional black-box neural networks in terms of interpretability, convergence speed, and training sample requirements.",
    "Krishnananthalingam et al. [283] developed a deep unfolding network to deal with the constant modulus waveform optimization problem for ISAC networks.",
    "They unfolded the projected gradient descent algorithm to a neural network with the sparsely connected architecture and trained it in a USL manner, achieving comparable performance and 30 times the running speed than the traditional algorithms."
  ],
